{"tid":1381492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抗 爭 受 傷 義 士 整 合","createTime":"2019-07-29T08:58:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T20:08:37.000Z","uid":52609,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2a395c57ac0cbe2bbe4f9954d93c40b585b3d98d","tid":1381492,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:58:04.000Z","msg":"想請大家幫手整合抗爭至現在受傷名單、一手或整合新聞已有資料都可以<br />\n我開始緊做，但因為太多資料，所以想請大家一齊幫手，<br />\n可直接喺POST下面直接貼或者tg我　<a href=\"https://t.me/injuries612\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finjuries612&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2BktrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=abf0480f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/injuries612</a><br />\n<br />\n需要資料：<br />\n（１）相／影片CAP圖／影片<br />\n（２）日期、受傷細節、受傷原因、受傷部分、Source<br />\n（３）（非必須）姓名、年齡、性別<br />\n<br />\n例子： 0612_橡膠子彈_眼部_AppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第一步：整合傷亡名單Excel（做緊）</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q7hYg9v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ7hYg9v.png&h=1e16759a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NnnA3PM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNnnA3PM.png&h=c3bf1e11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第二步：展示</span></span></strong><br />\n最後希望好似黃背心運動咁整成一張咁嘅圖／網站<br />\n將TVB唔敢播嘅流血畫面，展示出黎，貼哂出去連儂牆<br />\n唔好再比黑警啲所謂「非致命武器」呃人<br />\n令到更加多市民同情我地，令我地繼續有民意基礎打贏呢場仗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.liberation.fr/apps/2019/01/la-carte-des-gilets-jaunes-gravement-blesses/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.liberation.fr%2Fapps%2F2019%2F01%2Fla-carte-des-gilets-jaunes-gravement-blesses%2F&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2BktrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=ae13caaa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.liberation.fr/apps/2019/01/la-carte-des-gilets-jaunes-gravement-blesses/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.liberation.fr/checknews/2019/01/14/gilets-jaunes-le-decompte-des-blesses-graves_1702863\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.liberation.fr%2Fchecknews%2F2019%2F01%2F14%2Fgilets-jaunes-le-decompte-des-blesses-graves_1702863&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2BktrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=0d80afaf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.liberation.fr/checknews/2019/01/14/gilets-jaunes-le-decompte-des-blesses-graves_1702863</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-sQlHkgADUXE/XDE5Oo1W__I/AAAAAAABIGY/4e2EpAGEoc84BXcXAC2H2wg8OuITvN5MACLcBGAs/s640/gilets+jaunes+violence+polici%C3%A8re+compil+2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-sQlHkgADUXE%2FXDE5Oo1W__I%2FAAAAAAABIGY%2F4e2EpAGEoc84BXcXAC2H2wg8OuITvN5MACLcBGAs%2Fs640%2Fgilets%2Bjaunes%2Bviolence%2Bpolici%25C3%25A8re%2Bcompil%2B2.jpg&h=9bf1ee35&s={SIZE}\" />[/quote]"},{"pid":"9a0c474614cec9454fe30f64d33d22e4f3b34bf2","tid":1381492,"uid":52609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:58:54.000Z","msg":"呢個POST已睇左<br />\nTHANKS<br />\n<br />\n受傷人士現況集中帖<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1240949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1240949</a>"},{"pid":"24b0145fa5396e31e68c2d24226cb315401ad22b","tid":1381492,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:14:28.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"7b21ed32dd2708dc6d1ac6b8e157a2f46ed018ab","tid":1381492,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:31:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4be08c830a46f74c4a022947eb8415ebd63adc32","tid":1381492,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:31:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c90fc1993f5a079fdee2477d1410cef7771d6aad","tid":1381492,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:11:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"301d371a66c309